</add>strand en de weg<del seq="20200818151945" type="context" evidence="16-22">,  die mensen maken haar ook kwaad</del>.</seg>
                <seg><add seq="20200818151955" type="nt" evidence="26-91">Ze fronst naar de vrouw in de kleine bikini<add seq="20200818152355" type="context" evidence="262-269">, die </add><add seq="20200818152317" type="nt|continue" evidence="170-205">zich net loom heeft op<add seq="20200818152332" type="typo" evidence="212">g</add>ericht om <add seq="20200818152336" type="pre-context" evidence="214-228">de kleur van </add>haar </add><del seq="20200818152341" type="pre-context" evidence="230-236">, die</del><del seq="20200818152106" type="pre-context" evidence="91-109"> haar badhanddoek </del></add><del seq="20200818152123" type="pre-context" evidence="128-145"><add seq="20200818152108" type="nt|continue" evidence="110-127"> plat  op haar rug</add></del><del seq="20200818152207" type="pre-context" evidence="157-166"><add seq="20200818152126" type="nt|continue" evidence="146-156"> zich loom </add></del><add seq="20200818152343" type="nt|continue" evidence="238-258">buik te inspecteren.</add></seg>
